<H3>
<TI>

<s docid="FBIS3-59001" num="7"> French Senate: Schengen `Inapplicable' by 1 Feb</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-59001" num="8"> BR2601114694 Paris LE FIGARO in French 26 Jan 94 p 6</s>
</F>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-59001" num="9"> BR2601114694</s>
