<TI>

<s docid="FBIS3-39341" num="8"> Commissioner `Hopeful' on Schengen Agreement</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-39341" num="9"> BR1102150994 Brussels EUROPE in English 10 Feb 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY</s>
