<TI>

<s docid="FBIS3-57961" num="8"> Lamassoure on European Enlargement, Schengen</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-57961" num="9"> BR0301123894 Paris LE POINT in French 31 Dec 93 pp 24-25--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY</s>
</F>
