<TI>

<s docid="FBIS3-38434" num="7"> Lamassoure: Schengen Delay Due to Technical Problem</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-38434" num="8"> BR0202105894 Paris LIBERATION in French 2 Feb 94 p 4</s>
</F>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-38434" num="9"> BR0202105894</s>
